<!-- @format -->

Requirements

- PHP 8.3.30
- Composer
- Mysql(Recomendation v8.4.3)
- Untuk Windows aktifkan ekstensi php com_dotnet
- Untuk database harap dibuat dulu tanpa tabel

Installation

1. Clone the repository
2. Run `composer require twbs/bootstrap:5.3.8` and `composer require twbs/bootstrap-icons` to install dependencies
3. Run your server Xampp Or Laragon
4. Open `http://localhost/` in your browser
5. Setting koneksi ke database di pengaturan
